ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 223, Nova-Scotia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 223 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to NOVA SCOTIA with respect to the post-tropical storm Dorian that occurred from September 7 to 8, 2019.
